<p>Destroy an instance and all of its data and services.</p>
<h3>Synopsis</h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre>cast instances destroy [OPTIONS] NAME 
</pre></div>

<h3>Required Arguments</h3>
<p><strong>NAME</strong></p>
<p>The name of the instance to be destroyed</p>
<h3>Options</h3>
<p><strong>--remote</strong> &lt;remote&gt;, <strong>-r</strong> &lt;remote&gt;</p>
<p>The remote to use for this command</p>
